            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beef is in the oven, add your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>yeast</strong> to a jug with 20ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[30ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[40ml] </span><strong>warm water </strong>and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and mix it all together, then set aside for 5-8 min for the yeast to develop</p><p>Combine 70g <span class=\"text-purple\">[100g] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[140g]</span> <strong>flour</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>butter</strong> and use your fingers to mix it together to form a crumb (clean hands is the best way!) – this is your <strong>buttery crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1718367673637-x200.jpg",
