            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the dish has had 30 min, divide the <strong>dumpling mixture</strong> into 3<strong> </strong>small<strong> </strong>balls per person – these are your <strong>homemade</strong> <strong>thyme dumplings</strong></p><p>Remove the dish from the oven and top with the <strong>homemade</strong> <strong>thyme dumplings</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven, covered, for a final 35 min – this is your <strong>beef chuck stew with homemade thyme dumplings</strong></p><p>Reboil a full kettle</p>",
